testimonials.content: Of all of the celestial bodies that capture our attention and fascination as astronomers, none has a greater influence on life on planet Earth than itâs own satellite, the moon. When you think about it, we regard the moon with such powerful significance that unlike the moons of other planets which we give names, we only refer to our one and only orbiting orb as THE moon. It is not a moon. To us, it is the one and only moon.
